description:
SPSS v16.0.1

 PRODUCT DESCRIPTION

                          SPSS for Windows v16.0.1

   DATA ANALYSIS WITH COMPREHENSIVE STATISTICS SOFTWARE

   Solve business and research problems using SPSS, a statistical and data
   management package for analysts and researchers.

   SPSS and most of its add-on modules run on the most popular operating
   platforms: Windows, Mac, and Linux.

   SPSS provides you with a broad range of capabilities for the entire
   analytical process.

   With SPSS, you can generate decision-making information quickly using
   powerful statistics, understand and effectively present your results
   with high-quality tabular and graphical output, share your results
   with others using a variety of reporting methods, and take advantage
   of the analytical asset storage and deployment capabilities of other
   SPSS products.

   Results from your data analysis enable you to make smarter decisions
   more quickly by uncovering key facts, patterns, and trends.

<------------------------------------------------------------------------------>

   INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

   1. Unrar, Burn or mount

   2. If installer asks for Serial Number then use the keygen in the EDGE
      dir to generate one and complete installation until you get to the
      License Authorization Wizard.

   3. Select \"License my product now (recommended)\" then click Next.

   4. You will now be at the \"Overview of Licensensing\" screen, click Next.

   5. You will now be at the \"Enter Codes\" screen, now you should generate
      an Authorization Code with the keygen and use it, then click Next.

   6. You will now be at the \"Select Authorization Method\" screen, here you
      should select \"Telephone\" and then click Next.

   7. You are now at the \"Telephone Authorization\" screen, it will show you
      your Lock Code near the bottom of the window, enter this into the
      Lock Code fields in the keygen, select the Product/Feature you wish
      and now generate your License Code, press next in the Licensing Wizard
      and then copy this code into the License Code field.

   8. Enjoy.

   PS. If the Lock Code doesn\&#039;t start with 100 like we put in the keygen,
       you can just edit this field in the keygen to reflect your Lock Code
       first part.

       If you are installing SPSS main product you can add many additional
       features to the existing base license, just run the \"SPSS 16.0 License
       Authorization Wizard\" and add a new license with another feature you
       selected from the drop down.

       Thank you for flying EDGE airlines - Why patch when you can keygen?
